irsi insieme in un mondo virtuale."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":143,"tagline":"まだ誰も見たことがない「かぐや姫」の物語。","homepage":"https://www.cho-kaguyahime.com","overview":"月から逃げてきた自由奔放な少女・かぐやと暮らすことになった彩葉は、かぐやにねだられ、共に仮想空間でライバー活動を始める。だがかぐやには、地球に長く居られない理由が...。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Kaguya, princesse cosmique","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fr/title/81756595","overview":"La vie d'Iroha bascule lorsque Kaguya, une chanteuse insouciante qui a fui la Lune, emménage chez elle et la convainc de se produire ensemble dans un monde virtuel."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Kaguya: A Princesa Espacial","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81756595","overview":"A vida de Iroha sai da órbita quando a fugitiva Kaguya chega direto da lua e a convence a se apresentar com ela em um mundo virtual."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81756595","overview":"Życie Irohy wywraca się do góry nogami, gdy Kaguya — beztroska uciekinierka z Księżyca — wprowadza się do niej i namawia ją, by wspólnie występowały w wirtualnym świecie."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"超時空輝耀姬！","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81756595","overview":"彩葉遇見了逃離月球的輝耀姬，無憂無慮的輝耀姬搬進她家，還說服她一起在虛擬世界登台表演，讓彩葉的生活徹底脫離了常軌。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"超時空輝耀姬！","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81756595","overview":"彩葉遇見了逃離月球的輝耀姬，無憂無慮的輝耀姬搬進她家，還說服她一起在虛擬世界登台表演，讓彩葉的生活徹底脫離了常軌。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"초(超) 가구야 공주!","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/title/81756595","overview":"달에서 도망쳐 온, 자유분방한 가구야가 이로하의 집에 살게 되면서, 이로하의 삶은 궤도를 이탈할 지경이다. 게다가 가구야는 이로하에게 가상 세계에서 함께 무대에 서자고 설득한다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"La princesa Kaguya del cosmos","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81756595","overview":"La vida de Iroha se sale de órbita cuando Kaguya, una chica que viene de la Luna, se muda con ella y la convence de actuar juntas en un mundo virtual."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"超时空辉夜姬！","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在梦想与希望汇聚的虚拟空间“月读”，少女们相遇，以及离别的舞台，就此拉开帷幕——\r 在不远的未来，就读于东京都内重点高中的17岁少女酒寄彩叶，过着兼顾打工与学业的超忙碌生活。月见八千代是互联网虚拟空间“月读”的管理员兼超人气主播，彩叶平日透过观看她的直播放松身心。在这个任何人都能创造自己的分身，自由进行创作活动的“月读”里，彩叶一边支持着自己的偶像八千代，一边靠对战游戏零零散散赚点零用钱。\r 某天放学回家的路上，彩叶发现了一根闪烁着七彩光芒的电线杆，从里面钻出来的，竟是个极其可爱的婴儿。放心不下的彩叶将其带回了家，没想到对方转眼间长大，长成了与彩叶年纪相仿的少女。\r 「你……该不会是辉夜姬吧？」长大后的辉夜姬十分任性。在她那任性的请求下，彩叶开始帮她在月读开展主播活动。彩叶作为制作人创作音乐，而辉夜则作为主播负责演唱，两人也在合作中一点点拉近了距离。然而她们并不知道，一道不祥的阴影，为将辉夜带回月球，已悄然逼近——\r 这是一个，还从未有人见过的「辉夜姬」的故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"La princesa Kaguya del cosmos","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81756595","overview":"La vida de Iroha se sale de control cuando Kaguya, una despreocupada fugitiva de la Luna, se muda con ella y la convence para actuar juntas en un mundo virtual."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81756595","overview":"Irohas Leben gerät aus der Bahn, als Kaguya, eine Ausreißerin vom Mond, bei ihr einzieht und sie überredet, gemeinsam in einer virtuellen Welt aufzutreten."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"‫كاغويا أميرة الفضاء!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81756595","overview":"تخرج حياة \"إيروها\" عن مسارها حين تنتقل الفتاة الهانئة البال، والهاربة من القمر، \"كاغويا\" للعيش معها، وتقنعها بالغناء معها في عالم افتراضي."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"‫كاغويا أميرة الفضاء!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81756595","overview":"تخرج حياة \"إيروها\" عن مسارها حين تنتقل الفتاة الهانئة البال، والهاربة من القمر، \"كاغويا\" للعيش معها، وتقنعها بالغناء معها في عالم افتراضي."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Kosmická princezna Kaguja!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81756595","overview":"Iroha má novou spolubydlící Kaguju, která jí převrátí svět naruby. Tahle bezstarostná tulačka z Měsíce ji totiž přesvědčí, aby spolu vystupovaly ve virtuálním světě."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"超时空辉耀姬！","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81756595","overview":"无忧无虑的辉耀逃离了月球，和彩叶住在一起，并说服彩叶在虚拟世界一起表演，彩叶的生活轨迹从此彻底改变。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Kozmička princeza Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81756595","overview":"Irohin se život okrene naglavačke kad se doseli Kaguya, bezbrižna bjegunka s Mjeseca, koja je nagovori na zajednički nastup u virtualnom svijetu."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81756595","overview":"Het leven van Iroha raakt volledig uit balans als het zorgeloze, weggelopen maanmeisje Kaguya bij haar intrekt en haar overhaalt om samen op te treden in een virtuele wereld."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81756595","overview":"Irohas liv bliver slået ud af sit kredsløb, da Kaguya, en sorgløs, bortløben pige fra Månen, flytter ind og overbeviser hende om at optræde sammen i en virtuel verden."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"הנסיכה הקוסמית קאגויה","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81756595","overview":"קאגויה נמלטת מחייה המונוטוניים בירח, עוברת לגור עם אירוהה ומשכנעת אותה להופיע איתה בעולם וירטואלי – וחייה של אירוהה משתנים מקצה לקצה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81756595","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Κοσμική Πριγκίπισσα Καγκούγια!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81756595","overview":"Η ζωή της Ιρόχα ανατρέπεται όταν η Καγκούγια, μια ανέμελη φυγάς του φεγγαριού, μετακομίζει στη γειτονιά της και την πείθει να εμφανιστούν μαζί σε έναν εικονικό κόσμο."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Kaguya, princesse cosmique","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81756595","overview":"La vie d'Iroha est bouleversée quand Kaguya, une fugueuse insouciante de la Lune, entre dans sa vie et la convainc de devenir des vidéastes dans un monde virtuel."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81756595","overview":"Irohan elämä lähtee yllättäen uudelle kiertoradalle, kun huoleton Kuun karkulainen Kaguya tempaa hänet vetovoimallaan mukaansa virtuaalimaailmaan."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"A kozmikus Kaguya hercegnő","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81756595","overview":"Iroha élete teljesen új pályára áll, amikor Kaguya, egy szabad szellemű szökevény a Holdól hozzá költözik, és ráveszi, hogy szerepeljenek együtt egy virtuális világban."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81756595","overview":"Kehidupan Iroha kacau saat Kaguya, seorang pelarian yang berjiwa bebas dari Bulan, datang dan tinggal bersama, lalu meyakinkannya tampil di dunia virtual bersama-sama."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81756595","overview":"Kehidupan Iroha mula huru-hara selepas tinggal dengan Kaguya, pelarian yang berjiwa bebas dari bulan. Kaguya memujuknya agar membuat persembahan di dunia maya bersamanya."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81756595","overview":"Irohas liv blir snudd på hodet når Kaguya, en bekymringsløs rømling fra månen, flytter inn og overtaler henne til å opptre sammen i en virtuell verden."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Princesa Cósmica Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81756595","overview":"Iroha vê a vida sair de órbita quando Kaguya, uma descontraída fugitiva da Lua, vem viver com ela e a convence a participar num concurso num mundo virtual."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81756595","overview":"Irohas liv förändras för alltid när Kaguya, en frisinnad flicka som flytt från månen, flyttar in och övertalar henne att de ska framträda tillsammans i en virtuell värld."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmica prințesă Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81756595","overview":"Viața lui Iroha este dată peste cap când Kaguya, o fugară lipsită de griji de pe Lună, se mută la ea și o convinge să evolueze într-o lume virtuală."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81756595","overview":"Biglang nagbago ang buhay ni Iroha nang dumating si Kaguya, isang masayahing babae na tumakas mula sa Buwan, at kumbinsihin siyang mag-perform sila sa virtual world."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"Космическая принцесса Кагуя!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81756595","overview":"Жизнь Ирохи сходит с привычной орбиты, когда к ней подселяется Кагуя — беззаботная беглянка с Луны — и убеждает ее вместе выступать в виртуальном мире."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Cosmic Princess Kaguya!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81756595","overview":"Iroha'nın hayatı, Ay'dan kaçak olarak gelen kaygısız Kaguya'nın, onu sanal bir dünyada birlikte yaşamaya ikna etmesiyle yörüngesinden çıkar."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"เจ้าหญิงกระบอกไม้ไผ่ ในโลกเมตาเวิร์ส","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/th/title/81756595","overview":"ชีวิตของอิโรฮะมีอันต้องพลิกผัน เมื่อคางุยะผู้รักอิสระที่หนีมาจากดวงจันทร์ย้ายเข้ามาอยู่ด้วย และพยายามชักชวนให้เธอไปร่วมแสดงในโลกเสมือนด้วยกัน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Космічна принцеса Каґуя!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81756595","overview":"Життя Ірохи сходить зі звичної орбіти, коли безтурботна втікачка з Місяця Каґуя поселяється в неї та вмовляє її разом виступати у віртуальному світі."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Kaguya – Công chúa vũ trụ!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81756595","overview":"Cuộc sống của Iroha chệch khỏi quỹ đạo khi Kaguya, một cô gái phóng khoáng bỏ trốn khỏi mặt trăng, chuyển đến sống chung và thuyết phục cô cùng biểu diễn trong thế giới ảo."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"کاگویا شاهدخت کیهانی!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ایروهای هفده ساله میان مدرسه و کار پاره وقت مدام در رفت و آمد است. اما با ورود کاگویا دختری مرموز از ماه که ناگهان وارد زندگی اش می شود همه چیز دگرگون می شود..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":10228,"adult":false,"title":"Pokémon: The First Movie","video":false,"overview":"Determined to prove its superiority, a bio-engineered Pokémon called Mewtwo lures Ash, Pikachu and others into a Pokemon match like none before.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,14,28],"popularity":5.5007,"vote_count":1549,"poster_path":"/xPW3AeK3iQi1Zd9dCbdNLijE48o.jpg","release_date":"1998-07-18","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/eA0qc5ihjSKG05tdJO4QPgYPAwY.jpg","original_title":"劇場版ポケットモンスター ミュウツーの逆襲","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1259916,"adult":false,"title":"Reiteración","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[878,18],"popularity":0.1662,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/kprxGIVhN5feGkalreBv0t7e2w8.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-12","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Reiteración","original_language":"es"},{"id":470703,"adult":false,"title":"Body Jack: Sublime Separation","video":false,"overview":"A high schooler fulfills a lifelong fantasy after a high-tech device lets him slip into the body of his childhood crush's best friend.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.5498,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/yEzTCkU2eURPpxXBTFp6rHmkVJ5.jpg","release_date":"1987-01-28","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/tq7zViUEXnVzMfaYEeVEE0zuZT3.jpg","original_title":"ボディジャック 楽しい幽体離脱","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10353,"adult":false,"title":"The Visitors II: The Corridors of Time","video":false,"overview":"The sequel to The Visitors reunites us with those lovable ruffians from the French Medieval ages who - through magic - are transported into the present, with often drastic consequences. Godefroy de Montmirail travels to today to recover the missing family jewels and a sacred relic, guarantor of his wife-to-be's fertility. The confrontation between Godefroy's repellent servant Jack the Crack and his descendent, the effete Jacquart, present-day owner of the chateau, further complicates the matter.","genre_ids":[35,14],"popularity":0.8928,"vote_count":1050,"poster_path":"/c1xMb4GfTuyKSRUoeewBF27dtKa.jpg","release_date":"1998-02-11","vote_average":6.023,"backdrop_path":"/8PoskoYT4QQqE7MtExsK0oS9yp9.jpg","original_title":"Les Couloirs du temps : Les Visiteurs II","original_language":"fr"},{"id":10494,"adult":false,"title":"Perfect Blue","video":false,"overview":"Rising pop star Mima quits singing to pursue a career as an actress. After she takes up a role on a popular detective show, her handlers and collaborators begin turning up murdered. Harboring feelings of guilt and haunted by visions of her former self, Mima's reality and fantasy meld into a frenzied paranoia.","genre_ids":[16,53],"popularity":6.9414,"vote_count":3073,"poster_path":"/6WTiOCfDPP8XV4jqfloiVWf7KHq.jpg","release_date":"1998-02-28","vote_average":8.3,"backdrop_path":"/mHG7dpLb0ZScSY3LpP443IHRmjy.jpg","original_title":"PERFECT BLUE","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1067962,"adult":false,"title":"Bobby Loves Mangos","video":false,"overview":"A school principal finds a video from the future informing him of a bus accident that will kill 50 students.","genre_ids":[878,53],"popularity":0.1262,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1998-10-01","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Bobby Loves Mangos","original_language":"en"},{"id":472148,"adult":false,"title":"Saving Soldier Cashman","video":false,"overview":"An adaptation by V-Jump Festa of a one shot manga by Akira Toriyama.","genre_ids":[35,16,28,878],"popularity":0.4287,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/uN1JRQ97dbaCGXa1yAPYf84fsuW.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-29","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/goorhNAXWISSS2ANVPdgimAc1rn.jpg","original_title":"儲金戰士キャッシュマン","original_language":"ja"},{"id":664236,"adult":false,"title":"Extinct","video":false,"overview":"Op and Ed, two adorable donut-shaped animals - flummels - accidentally time-travel from 1835 to modern-day Shanghai.  There they discover traffic, trans fats, and worst of all, that flummels are now extinct. It's up to this bumbling pair to save themselves and their species...and, just maybe, change the course of history.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,12],"popularity":4.0985,"vote_count":181,"poster_path":"/kchu0regBPDjWORUzvTblyoA5aE.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-11","vote_average":6.257,"backdrop_path":"/yd2xws5wVT2Ss6f0Q0oTkdYtiQE.jpg","original_title":"Extinct","original_language":"en"},{"id":11957,"adult":false,"title":"Peut-être","video":false,"overview":"Arthur is invited to a New Year's Eve party to celebrate the year 2000. His girlfriend Lucie would like a baby from him but he refuses. Through the ceiling of the toilets, he discovers a passage leading to this futurist Paris. There, he meets an old man Ako who affirms he is his son and that he wants to exist. Otherwise he will vanish into the air. Arthur is still hesitant because his life is an unfulfilled one: a has a little lucrative job, is uncertain about his future and things are getting out of hand when Ako discovers the passage and interferes in the party.","genre_ids":[878,18],"popularity":0.9386,"vote_count":78,"poster_path":"/crHfjsE7ZE8yMa7bilCLbOsaHZY.jpg","release_date":"1999-11-10","vote_average":5.282,"backdrop_path":"/a8jKGQfOeAzgcMwLfaydkefGMQc.jpg","original_title":"Peut-être","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1262549,"adult":false,"title":"Give It All","video":false,"overview":"A high-school girl, Etsuko, just spends her days without any aims or purpose, until one day, Riina, a transfer student, asks her help to set up a boat club. Although Etsuko reluctantly accepts after hearing Riina speak passionately about her dream, she gradually starts to embrace the club after spending time with her teammates.","genre_ids":[16,18],"popularity":0.6037,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/5SsUC6HUq999flyBO5UNnlyQCep.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-25","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/tBEWseHXJxMCytk00QNLYAVfyG8.jpg","original_title":"がんばっていきまっしょい","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12140,"adult":false,"title":"Ghost in the Shell 2: Innocence","video":false,"overview":"Cyborg detective Batou is assigned to investigate a series of murders committed by gynoids—doll-like cyborgs, which all malfunctioned, killed, then self-destructed afterwards. The brains of the gynoids initialize in order to protect their manufacturer's software, but in one gynoid, which Batou himself neutralized, one file remains: a voice speaking the phrase \"Help me.\"","genre_ids":[16,18,878],"popularity":2.2568,"vote_count":952,"poster_path":"/1ZJRbLDVr90KLtKdmTT4WZhT26E.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-06","vote_average":7.334,"backdrop_path":"/8Cbzx17QdJ6xBx2uDkdlpWsemGg.jpg","original_title":"イノセンス","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12429,"adult":false,"title":"Ponyo","video":false,"overview":"When Sosuke, a young boy who lives on a clifftop overlooking the sea, rescues a stranded goldfish named Ponyo, he discovers more than he bargained for. Ponyo is a curious, energetic young creature who yearns to be human, but even as she causes chaos around the house, her father, a powerful sorcerer, schemes to return Ponyo to the sea.","genre_ids":[16,14,10751],"popularity":6.7888,"vote_count":4710,"poster_path":"/yp8vEZflGynlEylxEesbYasc06i.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-19","vote_average":7.757,"backdrop_path":"/shqLeIkqPAAXM8iT6wVDiXUYz1p.jpg","original_title":"崖の上のポニョ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":472689,"adult":false,"title":"The Monster Kid: Invitation to Monster Land","video":false,"overview":"Kaibutsu Taro, also known as Kaibutsu-kun, the prince of Monster Land. Hiroshi-kun, a human boy who is close to him, takes advantage of winter vacation to head to Kaibutsu-kun's hometown, Monster Land. However, humans are strictly prohibited from visiting Monster Land, and Hiroshi-kun, who breaks the rules, is turned into stone by the power of the eyes of Kaibutsu-kun's father, the Monster King! Kaibutsu-kun goes to retrieve the secret medicine \"Flower of Life\" in order to restore Hiroshi-kun to his normal state. But that flower...","genre_ids":[16,35,27,10751],"popularity":0.2784,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/yx1b9MQX26OlsUWRzXQjJWhKQAE.jpg","release_date":"1981-01-01","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/l1dfWAKkC8p2JWXurQCJzQWmSMJ.jpg","original_title":"怪物くん 怪物ランドへの招待","original_language":"ja"},{"id":472668,"adult":false,"title":"The Monster Kid and The Demon's Sword","video":false,"overview":"Kaibutsu-kun's father, the Great Monster King, suddenly complains of pain in his chest and collapses. It turns out that the rival Demon King has placed a curse on him with the \"Demon Sword\". Kaibutsu-kun and his three companions head into enemy territory, Demon Land. Prince Demokin, the son of the Great Demon King, appears. Out of curiosity, he invites the monsters to the temple where the demon sword is located.","genre_ids":[16,35,27],"popularity":0.4022,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/7sTnUspqTlpYSdKpsr98RypmUPx.jpg","release_date":"1982-03-13","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/lPQDxHLsJjjtwc7KebMHYcE6XLi.jpg","original_title":"怪物くん デーモンの剣","original_language":"ja"},{"id":472516,"adult":false,"title":"The Moment You Fall in Love","video":false,"overview":"Following Natsuki Enomoto's confession rehearsals with Yuu Setoguchi, their younger siblings Kotarou and Hina struggle to confess their own love. Despite a disastrous first meeting in middle school with her upperclassman Koyuki Ayase, Hina’s heart is captured by his warm smile. Initially confused by these newfound feelings, Hina soon realizes that she has fallen in love for the very first time.  Chasing after her brother Yuu and her crush Koyuki, Hina also enrolls in Sakuragaoka High School; but the threads of love are far-reaching, and they entangle Hina and her friends. Boisterous but sensitive, Hina hopes to confess her feelings to the tender-hearted Koyuki. Meanwhile, Kotarou, oblivious to his own feelings for her, is determined to always keep Hina smiling.  This movie follows Hina, Kotarou, and Koyuki in high school. Their youthful love forges new relationships, but also threatens to break others.","genre_ids":[18,16,10749,35],"popularity":1.0436,"vote_count":137,"poster_path":"/b3NQEmgAYKTDuAXSE0f294lrE4Q.jpg","release_date":"2016-12-17","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/lTbYegQ35QRWlWvDqYwS0okFiY4.jpg","original_title":"好きになるその瞬間を。～告白実行委員会～","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12580,"adult":false,"title":"Izo","video":false,"overview":"Izo is an assassin in the service of a Tosa lord and Imperial supporter. After killing dozens of the Shogun's men, Izo is captured and crucified. Instead of being extinguished, his rage propels him through the space-time continuum to present-day Tokyo. Here Izo transforms himself into a new, improved killing machine.","genre_ids":[28,18,14],"popularity":1.5837,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/rr2i9pba5sUieXoycquuNk1I4WN.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-07","vote_average":6.09,"backdrop_path":"/goV5xvp99pu3P4CFFYW40hZHW4g.jpg","original_title":"イゾー","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12599,"adult":false,"title":"Pokémon the Movie 2000","video":false,"overview":"When Lawrence III's scheme to capture the Legendary Pokémon Lugia upsets the balance of nature, it is up to Ash Ketchum and his friends to save the world.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,878,10751],"popularity":3.9784,"vote_count":913,"poster_path":"/6u65C8aG4krAVyHsTjAMF7ucTDH.jpg","release_date":"1999-07-17","vote_average":6.722,"backdrop_path":"/bS93S5uEVZng4qmDhmDMXTSEuay.jpg","original_title":"劇場版ポケットモンスター 幻のポケモン ルギア爆誕","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12600,"adult":false,"title":"Pokémon 4Ever","video":false,"overview":"In order to escape a greedy Pokémon hunter, Celebi must use the last of its energy to travel through time to the present day. Celebi brings along Sammy, a boy who had been trying to protect it. Along with Ash, Pikachu, and the rest of the gang, Sammy and Celebi must encounter an enemy far more advanced than the hunter, with the fate of the forest hanging in the balance.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,878,10751],"popularity":2.3823,"vote_count":449,"poster_path":"/thz83PS9twtVBEEAM59J1bh75nU.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-06","vote_average":6.468,"backdrop_path":"/lnwNzJdU4gMlgoQlaT8HgSI2OpD.jpg","original_title":"劇場版ポケットモンスター セレビィ 時を超えた遭遇","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12609,"adult":false,"title":"Help! I'm a Fish","video":false,"overview":"Three children are accidentally transformed into fish after consuming a potion made by an eccentric scientist. The kids end up in the sea, with one problem: they must 